        },
        "dataUid": "uid-3"
      },
      {
        "sourceTag": "text",
        "type": "custom",
        "children": [
          "Have the most pieces when the board fills up or no moves remain for either player."
        ],
        "properties": {
          "fontsize": "10",
          "color": "#cccccc",
          "width": "240"
        },
        "dataUid": "uid-4"
      },
      {
        "sourceTag": "text",
        "type": "custom",
        "children": [
          "Rules"
        ],
        "properties": {
          "fontsize": "12",
          "color": "#ffaa00"
        },
        "dataUid": "uid-5"
      },
      {
        "sourceTag": "text",
        "type": "custom",
        "children": [
          "Place a piece to outflank opponent pieces between your new piece and an existing one. Outflanked pieces flip to your color."
        ],
        "properties": {
          "fontsize": "10",
          "color": "#cccccc",
          "width": "240"
        },
        "dataUid": "uid-6"
      },
      {
        "sourceTag": "text",
        "type": "custom",
        "children": [
          "Flanking works in all 8 directions. You must flip at least one piece to play."
        ],
        "properties": {
          "fontsize": "10",
          "color": "#cccccc",
          "width": "240"
        },
        "dataUid": "uid-7"
      },
      {
        "sourceTag": "text",
        "type": "custom",
        "children": [
          "Strategy"
        ],
        "properties": {
          "fontsize": "12",
          "color": "#ffaa00"
        },
        "dataUid": "uid-8"
      },
      {
        "sourceTag": "text",
        "type": "custom",
        "children": [
          "Corners never flip - capture them! Avoid cells next to empty corners. Control edges for stability."
        ],
        "properties": {
          "fontsize": "10",
          "color": "#cccccc",
          "width": "240"
        },
        "dataUid": "uid-9"
      },
      {
        "sourceTag": "text",
        "type": "custom",
        "children": [
          "Controls"
        ],
        "properties": {
          "fontsize": "12",
          "color": "#ffaa00"
        },
        "dataUid": "uid-10"
      },
      {
        "sourceTag": "text",
        "type": "custom",
        "children": [
          "Click highlighted cells to place pieces. Use PASS when no moves are available."
